headline: Madison Reed Hair Color Makes International Debut with Ulta Beauty Launch in Mexico
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, September 10, 2025--Madison Reed, the prestige beauty brand revolutionizing the hair color industry in the U.S., today announced its global expansion with the launch of its salon-quality hair color in Ulta Beauty's inaugural international location in Mexico City, Mexico.
